sequenceDiagram
    participant State
    participant Chain as Chain Check
    participant DescEng as Desc Engine

    Note over State: Cycle 0: IDLE
    Note over State: Cycle 1: FETCH_DESC
    Note over State: Cycle 2-N: XFER_DATA
    Note over State: Cycle N+1: COMPLETE
    State->>Chain: Check next_descriptor_ptr != 0
    Chain-->>State: Pointer valid
    Note over State: Cycle N+2: NEXT_DESC
    State->>DescEng: Fetch next descriptor
    DescEng-->>State: Descriptor valid/ready
    Note over State: Cycle N+3: FETCH_DESC
    Note over State: Cycle N+4+: XFER_DATA (next transfer)
